item.title: [+957] Bank forecloses on home that had been fully paid for in cash
item.description: Yes, it was Bank of America. A Massachusetts couple paid for their future retirement home in Florida with cash in 2005, five years before agents for the bank seized the house -- they got the address wrong -- removed belongings and changed the locks on the doors, according to a lawsuit.
